---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/ui/Section.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Grief & Loss Therapy | Better Lives Building Tribes"
  description="Compassionate grief and loss therapy to help you navigate loss, express emotions, build coping strategies, and find healing."
>
  <Section padding="lg">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>Grief &amp; Loss Therapy</h1>
      <p>
        The journey through grief and loss can often feel like navigating a stormy sea.
        At Better Lives Building Tribes, we are dedicated to creating a safe harbor where
        you can freely express your emotions. Healing is not a straightforward path; it is
        a deeply personal journey that unfolds uniquely for each individual.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="cream" padding="md">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <h2>Expression &amp; Validation</h2>
      <p>
        We provide a safe, non-judgmental space for you to express your feelings around
        grief and loss. We believe in acknowledging all of your emotions — whether it's
        sadness, anger, confusion, or even relief. Through various forms of expression
        including storytelling and art, we help you process what you're experiencing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section padding="md">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <h2>Coping Strategies</h2>
      <p>
        We offer practical techniques for managing anxiety, building resilience, and
        fostering a positive mindset during difficult times. Our approaches include
        mindfulness practices, creative expression, and community support to help you
        develop sustainable ways to cope with your loss.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="cream" padding="md">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <h2>Building Resilience &amp; Hope</h2>
      <p>
        Our services emphasize resilience, hope, and cherishing memories. We help you
        find meaning and strength as you navigate your grief journey, supporting you
        in honoring what you've lost while moving toward healing and renewed purpose.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="teal" padding="lg">
    <div class="cta">
      <h2>Schedule a Free Consultation</h2>
      <p>
        You don't have to walk this path alone. Our compassionate therapists are here
        to support you through grief and loss.
      </p>
      <Button href="/schedule" variant="primary" size="lg">Book a Consultation</Button>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: var(--color-teal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .service-detail {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .service-detail h2 {
    color: var(--color-teal);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .service-detail p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .cta {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .cta p {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
